Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.48,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:06.68,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Things got a little hectic \Nin central Flognarde,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.19,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,but now it's all back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:12.72,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,The demon incident that occurred in \Nthe south at the Dragon's Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.43,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,was safely resolved by the Heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:19.04,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,who'd happened to be there at the time, and \Nan expedition by the three-country alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.60,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Peace returned to the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.82,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,and the hero Shinku was able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:27.43,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,come back with the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:32.26,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,The folks at Galette went \Nback with Hero Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.86,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Leo-sama and Prince Gaul\Nwere worried about Nanami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:39.23,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,so now they're relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.32,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,The folks at Pastillage are flying home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:47.77,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Cou-sama and Rebecca-san are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:49.90,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,both happy they can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:54.02,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,They've got plans for \Ntheir vacation, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:36.26,DogDays-ep-title,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)\an3}What's Passed On
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.93,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.49,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.54,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for our morning walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.41,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.67,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all ready for our walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.30,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.05,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.57,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I got up early because I was looking \Nforward to our walk so much, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.15,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's head out on our walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:34.12,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.21,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nanami already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.99,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's already in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:44.99,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,She's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.10,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.31,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.81,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.23,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:22.82,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's the new walk spot I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.26,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's play then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.15,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.65,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.34,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,And it smells so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.93,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Rose Daydream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.84,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a massage oil popular in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.19,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoulders... aren't that stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.10,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.93,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your hips and legs are stiff, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.61,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to rest on \Nthe expedition yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:04.17,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You came at top speed from \NGalette for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.74,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Leo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.18,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it wasn't just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:13.25,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you and Shinku and the \Ncreatures in the Dragon's Forest were all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.75,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a national broadcast \Nafter this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.30,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm going to share the details of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.65,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,what happened in the Dragon's Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.85,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Large expeditions put stress \Nand worry on the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:33.14,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I have a duty to explain \Nto them what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.71,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,and what the results were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.65,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough being a ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:42.58,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, only a very few think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.17,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Our activities are of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.29,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,great interest to the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.40,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,so I have to share
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.02,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,everything with the whole continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.16,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.58,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to make your skin and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.67,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,hair sparkle so people can \Ntell on the broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.77,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.52,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.45,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:15.64,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:41.96,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.27,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.79,DogDays-main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.72,DogDays-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! As much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.82,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I just have this feeling that the \NHero is being rude to the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:58.35,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're having fun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.88,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to play with the Hero, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.97,DogDays-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure it'll be your turn \Nto play with him once he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.86,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to be on the \Nbroadcast besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.69,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be Violet, from our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.58,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,and several military pundits
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.43,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,from Biscotti and Pastillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:22.45,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.50,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.54,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get a chance to thank Adel-sama for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:32.01,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,the Spirit Crystal she gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.33,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:38.10,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,you missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.00,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not go see her today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.02,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.42,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,The three Genoise are heading
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.85,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,to Pastillage on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.96,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You can go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.24,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Noir, Jaune, Vert,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.79,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,take Nanami with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.41,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.67,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Leo-sama is so sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.17,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You look more wonderful than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.92,DogDays-main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a treatment later, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.28,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.83,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Couver, the hall seems
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.69,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,very lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.07,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.07,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,There's some kind of fall merchant's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.15,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,They're announcing the new weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.57,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,and armor for the war games.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.41,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.78,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.03,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.04,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's called a florentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.32,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cookie from France!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.63,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,France is an Earth country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.80,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.92,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.04,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any cute cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:02.22,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,like this when I was on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.94,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but it still reminds me of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:11.05,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to these cute cookies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.81,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and this cute Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.25,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,that I can touch the memories \Nof the place I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.85,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, I'll bring more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.28,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.47,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.89,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,As a new Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.33,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,there's things I'd like to \Nlearn from the original Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.33,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.90,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,The first Hero in modern Flognarde,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.19,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hero King who saved the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.91,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.80,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.40,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestor is the pride of Pastillage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.35,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are making \Ntoo big a deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.95,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We just helped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.36,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the continent recover a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.59,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The name and position of Hero King
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.24,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,were something they gave me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.82,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.74,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Callaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.12,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Nanami is coming from Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.00,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:09.00,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to thank Adel-sama \Nfor yesterday, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.13,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.00,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,So where's she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.41,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.26,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Adel-sama! Cou-sama!  \NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.90,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.97,DogDays-overlap,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They're almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.62,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ancestor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.73,DogDays-main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.73,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Adel-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:35.61,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you once \Nagain for the Spirit Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.18,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you can use it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.86,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.87,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That crystal borrows the \Npower of the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:46.74,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same type as one used by
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.62,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,someone very dear to me:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.87,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the princess who brought me here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:57.26,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the last ruler of the Kingdom of Pastillage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.16,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered the one she had,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.26,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and recreated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.14,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You looked very pretty \Nafter transforming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.27,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.95,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was taller and my hair changed color...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.02,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I gave my Hero Crystal to Shinku and Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.77,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I gave the Demon Crystal \NValerie had to Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:19.28,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And you get her Spirit Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.12,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of that:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.39,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,the story of the first Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.92,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The princess and the Hero \Nand the Demon King combined
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.84,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,their three powers to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.83,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,defeat the demons and bring peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.79,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story of Heroes \Ntold all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.34,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:40.17,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, that was a job a Hero did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.36,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The world is really peaceful now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.61,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but the most important part of being a Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.56,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.69,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's to bring smiles to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.09,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,So I hope you'll all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:09.22,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting this service \Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.16,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.14,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.21,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This weird squishy thing \Njumped on me all of sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.59,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Squishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.77,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This way, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.15,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.53,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Adel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.03,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.02,DogDays-internal,V,0000,0000,0000,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:43.66,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.11,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You were raising Muni-Muni, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.31,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Muni-Muni?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:50.69,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Muni-Muni are a quickly multiplying \Nmonster that attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.84,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.33,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Adel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a fair way to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.55,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What other way am I supposed to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:08.01,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Those things don't hurt people!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.51,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,They just eat cloth and metal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.32,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Cloth and metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.23,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.90,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,They especially like things soaked \Nwith human sweat and bodily fluids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.52,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.52,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,When I was Demon King,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.78,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'd put them right near \Nthe entrance to dungeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.21,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're very convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.18,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They'd melt and eat the weapons and clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.22,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,of the people who were \Nso eager to attack me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.30,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and make them lose their will \Nto fight and drive them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.29,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I agree that's convenient, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:43.10,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need them anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.03,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,so you promised to put them \Nin the sealed box, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.55,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.55,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Lately that idiot Leasha and her friends \Nhave been getting one over on me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:55.68,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,And so I thought I'd use them \Nto get back at them a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.40,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.32,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:07.59,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If they're after armor and clothes, \Nis the knights barracks in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.59,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The event hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:13.13,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,It's not knights participating \Nin the event, it's models!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.08,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.11,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:18.83,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.34,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Knight Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.46,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The demons appeared here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.46,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but the ones that showed up \Nat the barracks we defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.72,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Leasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.47,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading for the hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.72,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.77,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.03,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.74,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,And really fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.36,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,If they keep multiplying \Nand head out into town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.63,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.37,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.58,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:56.95,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.18,DogDays-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.21,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.78,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.79,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you control them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.79,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I can try,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.22,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not like they're that smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.56,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.19,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We can't cause problems for other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.30,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We need to resolve this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.60,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.87,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.43,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.72,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.24,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.83,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:50.57,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.12,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.21,DogDays-main,Co,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.05,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Genoise were defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.28,DogDays-main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear Cou-sama's \Ngunfire anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.92,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The speed at which they multiply is fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.05,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.82,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.48,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Valerie! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.28,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.21,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.03,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the Spirit, the Demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.63,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,and the Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.17,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,If we combine the three of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.26,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,it may just work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.39,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.64,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.77,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Crystal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.40,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.40,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.34,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Demon King Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.92,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.34,DogDays-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.22,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Shine, purifying light!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:35.82,DogDays-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:15.27,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait... seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.78,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,Even if those were low-rank demons, \Nthey turned them into spirits in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.04,DogDays-main,V,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen anybody pull off a \Nstunt like that since my sister did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:40.46,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,The show was given extra time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.80,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,and was back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:46.55,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was hurt and the building wasn't \Nas badly damaged as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.06,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Callaway-san had a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.11,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,hard time dealing with it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.31,DogDays-narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm taking him something later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:58.57,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've really caused problems for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:20:59.99,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.55,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we're sorry for not being useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.20,DogDays-main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We're useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.53,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.06,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I did something amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.33,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.71,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.47,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But it's thanks to the Spirit Crystal \Nand Demon Crystal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.21,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.35,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It was a dangerous situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:23.74,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but because the power of \Nthe Hero, Spirit, and Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:26.20,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,worked together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.22,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.25,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.85,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,of old times...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.54,DogDays-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Valerie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:37.67,DogDays-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.58,DogDays-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him since this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.70,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Adel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.96,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Adel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:53.25,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I feel really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.33,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.78,DogDays-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,No playing tricks, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:33.49,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:35.87,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:38.24,DogDays-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll play with us next time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.93,DogDays-next-ep-title,Episode 5,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}Exploration at \Nthe Crystal Mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.24,0:23:39.59,DogDays-main-top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:41.93,DogDays-next-ep-title,,0000,0000,0000,,
